<plot>Religion against Religion, country against country, wars are waged, innocents die, and a generation is lost. Set around a backdrop of a psychological thriller, it questions one's perception of what is right and what is wrong. It's a story about an immoral husband who cheats, a pregnant wife who turns toward violence, and a priest who fights for his perception of the right. It's a story about the young generation lost in the act of war.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016504</url></doc>
